CO2 Traders May Establish ‘Trusted Account’ List

-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 
2011-05-06T08:21:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/co2-traders-may-establish-trusted-account-list-correct-.html
Carbon traders including airlines can
establish a “trusted account list” in the European Union
registry starting June 30, 2012, according to a proposal of the
EU commission in Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
